{"tid":1892204,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"三年內由爭啲破產到賺到百萬既血汗史","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T22:56:19.000Z","uid":166403,"like":149,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"670ea97af9342ec5356e6d9271ca19400c6cb9df","tid":1892204,"uid":166403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"三年前遇人不淑，嫁咗個唔爭氣既ex<br />\n輸錢輸到要賣嫁妝，爭啲破埋產<br />\n絕望到諗過死<br />\n好彩上黎連登同大家呻<br />\n最後鼓起畢生最大嘅勇氣離婚<br />\n<br />\n由戶口得返五十蚊<br />\n捱到三年後既今日見到7位數<br />\n仲遇到個真正細心體貼願意一齊奮斗努力既另一半<br />\n如無意外出年可以買樓結婚生b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重回人生正軌<br />\n<br />\n所以仲糾纏係無將來既關係既巴絲打<br />\n希望你地都有離開嘅勇氣<br />\n<br />\n信我，下個會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee23977ab4eaaf27070dc9d3333ab6a6fd7bcd51","tid":1892204,"uid":76747,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"READ."},{"pid":"58419d589f9f798154a655aa0442060fdc6e34ff","tid":1892204,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"A0lm"},{"pid":"1912d42a6224b877366c9ecaedc2e0d90468ddc0","tid":1892204,"uid":227275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"講多d好冇"},{"pid":"2db8c7bb71447240e25d5eedd53e8b2cfab0304d","tid":1892204,"uid":64131,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"好易姐， $20 推廿口"},{"pid":"70fdb1e75443e30221ac891414dda15c070a680b","tid":1892204,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"絲打 or 巴打"},{"pid":"ec40556dca0226d340f7a1ae1ff8f52c302985c9","tid":1892204,"uid":49628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"點賺的"},{"pid":"395da5dc6e91ad037f2f348a66c4dca5d5ece2b6","tid":1892204,"uid":27362,"like":44,"dislike":6,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"好感人 